==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unclinch
<hw>Un*clinch"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>clinch</ets>.]</ety> <def>To cause to be no longer
clinched; to open; <as>as, to <ex>unclinch</ex> the fist</as>.</def>
<altsp>[Written also <asp>unclench</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

